      • getRowColPair

        public static int[] getRowColPair(com.github.bhlangonijr.chesslib.Square sq)
        This function converts the E7 format of the library to a tuple of integers. It returns B7 as follows: B7: {6, 1}, whereas the B is the second element, and 7 turns into the, by one, decremented row
        Parameters:
        sq - The square, which should be converted
        Returns:
        The tuple specifying the row and column or null.
